						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Making-agriculture-more-appealing-to-the-youth" title="Making agriculture more appealing to the youth" alt="link">Making agriculture more appealing to the youth</a></h2>

	
					<p> 
In this inverview, Robert Sabiiti, Uganda’s representative to the UN agencies responsible for food and agriculture shares insights on the steps being taken by Uganda to make agriculture more appealing to youth. Sabiiti, who works in Uganda’s Ministry of Agriculture, Animal Industry and Fisheries, describes the steps being taken in Uganda in to attract university youths to agriculture.Source: African Executive, 9 May 2007. </p>
							<p><span class="date">18/07/2007</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Making-agriculture-more-appealing-to-the-youth">Read more...</a>
